{"parents": [{"link": "../../", "title": "Teams"}], "prev": {"link": "../enable_a_user/", "title": "Users: Enabling a User"}, "next": {"link": "../import_users/", "title": "Users: Importing Users"}, "title": "Groups: Managing a Group", "meta": null, "body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"groups-managing-a-group\">\n<h1>Groups: Managing a Group<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#groups-managing-a-group\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<div class=\"line-block\">\n<div class=\"line\"><strong>Groups</strong> allows you to group users of your organization together under a leader.</div>\n<div class=\"line\">This feature can be helpful when you interact with other apps of the Maha Platform.</div>\n<div class=\"line\">For example, if you want to give a number of people access to folders in your <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/drive/guides/interacting_with_a_file.html\">drive</a> , you can <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/team/guides/setting_up_group.html\">create a group</a> with these users to grant them view privileges in an efficient manner.</div>\n</div>\n<ol class=\"arabic simple\">\n<li><p>Click <i class=\"fa fa-bars\"></i> in the ribbon</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Team</strong></p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Groups</strong></p></li>\n<li><p>Click a group to view group members</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <i class=\"fa fa-ellipsis-v\"></i> and <strong>Edit Group</strong> to <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/general/guides/functions_of_the_grid/how_to_edit.html\">edit</a> the group</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <i class=\"fa fa-ellipsis-v\"></i> and <strong>Manage Users</strong> to add users to and/or remove users from the group</p>\n<ul class=\"simple\">\n<li><p>Select user(s) you would like to assign to the group</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <i class=\"fa fa-times\"></i> to remove a user</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Save</strong></p></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n", "metatags": "", "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["users/team/guides/import_users", "Users: Importing Users", "N", "next"], ["users/team/guides/enable_a_user", "Users: Enabling a User", "P", "previous"]], "sourcename": "users/team/guides/groups.rst.txt", "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">Groups: Managing a Group</a></li>\n</ul>\n", "display_toc": false, "page_source_suffix": ".rst", "current_page_name": "users/team/guides/groups", "sidebars": ["localtoc.html", "relations.html", "sourcelink.html", "searchbox.html"], "customsidebar": null, "favicon_url": null, "logo_url": null, "alabaster_version": "0.7.12"}